{"tid":2377144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國派出8架轟炸機 4架重型戰機入侵台灣防空識別區 疑似針對靠近台灣的美國航空母艦","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T12:38:20.000Z","uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bd3bbc4cad763d0104a363ad297a320af7ec70","tid":2377144,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"根據廣播紀錄，共機今天極度罕見地，在短短2小時內入侵我空域高達7次，短時間內密集擾台，相當值得注意。而稍早國防部也證實中共軍機包括運-8反潛機1架、轟-6K機8架、殲-16機4架一共13架擾台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4F9kZo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4F9kZo.jpg&h=9d8e9e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自上午10時左右至13時30分止，空軍各基地至少緊急起飛15批次（30架機）前往攔截監控。另外，美國海軍C-2灰狗式艦載型運輸機現蹤巴士海峽，疑似為美國航母通過巴士海峽。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?p=77954&amp;title=國防消息&amp;SelectStyle=即時軍事動態\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mnd.gov.tw%2FPublish.aspx%3Fp%3D77954%26title%3D%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%26SelectStyle%3D%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%85%8B&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=3eb75152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?p=77954&amp;title=國防消息&amp;SelectStyle=即時軍事動態</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=886921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D886921&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=3072e08a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D886921&h=4513c9b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=886921</a>"},{"pid":"e0878bd4990033e51dcf6475c6293aaa27e6d205","tid":2377144,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\